    <searchtitle>Supporting Information: National Tariff Payment System - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>
 is managed by 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_improvement">NHS Improvement</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>
 sets out the national tariff for each year.        </p>
      <p>
This set of prices and rules helps local 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Groups</xref>
 work with 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Providers</xref>, such as 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_trust">NHS Trusts</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_foundation_trust">NHS Foundation Trusts</xref>
 to identify which health care 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 provide best value to their 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>, see the:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
               <p>
 website at: 
                                <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/resources/pay-syst/"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">NHS payment system</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
gov.uk website at: 
                                <xref href="https://improvement.nhs.uk/resources/national-tariff/"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">The NHS payment system: documents and guidance.</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
